cast.overview: A teenager who's lived a sheltered life because she's allergic to everything, falls for the boy who moves in next door.
cast.title: Everything, Everything

details.biography: Danube Hermosillo is a television, feature film, commercial, and voice-over actress. She moved to Los Angeles to pursue her dream of a career in the TV & film industry in 2015 and has worked in front of the camera ever since. Danube has booked a variety of leading and supporting roles in network television, studio feature films, and more. Working on big sets as an actress inspired her to venture behind the camera as well. Danube is more than a working actress; now she can also add screenwriter and producer to her skill set.
details.name: Danube R. Hermosillo
